{"tid":621961,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"預祝自己生日快樂","createTime":"2018-04-08T17:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T06:00:24.000Z","uid":41315,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1b405d380720be8eaeac9c0a8700bf886f1c9d45","tid":621961,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T17:40:12.000Z","msg":"願望係 我唔期望好人有好報<br />\n但閪人, 係應該要有閪報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢世仔未遇過一個咁自私既人<br />\n同你識左咁耐<br />\n就不斷咁開解你同你傾心事<br />\n第一晚見你就已經幾個人陪你傾心事通宵<br />\n中間你有幾多唔開心<br />\n有邊一次我地無陪你<br />\n有啲咩事俾人屌, 我幫你頂<br />\n背後俾人插左幾多野, 我都數唔到<br />\n最近你公司人事有問題<br />\n我又教你做人處事手法<br />\n就算我係忙, 都會聽你呷<br />\n<br />\n不過換來既係 反轉肚豬就係屎<br />\n好處你就識拎<br />\n有價值既你就識拎<br />\n責任呢 ? 你從來唔洗負亦唔會去負<br />\n剩係識得諗人地針對你對你唔好<br />\n<br />\n仲可以大條道理講出口話呢個責任你唔負, 只係會拎好處<br />\n到底講出口果下會唔會面紅 ?<br />\n<br />\n真心, 未試返咁樣俾一個 &quot;朋友&quot; 唔尊重到咁樣既地步<br />\n<br />\n人不犯我, 我不犯人<br />\n但你已經越過我底線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1003933b7583109e0e39049884963b25e04ab8dd","tid":621961,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T17:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小狗<br />\n生日快樂啊"},{"pid":"3f86a57218f88aa1ae97c5dc363e44bdd8097583","tid":621961,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1003933b7583109e0e39049884963b25e04ab8dd","tid":621961,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T17:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小狗<br />\n生日快樂啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T17:41:42.000Z","msg":"其實仲有 10日先生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a8de82d17f11bdd85c133b955c4b863de7f2c4","tid":621961,"uid":20122,"like":0,"dislike":0